jt-pve-storage-netapp (0.1.5-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Template Support Release
  * New Feature: Full Template Support
    - Implemented create_base method for VM-to-template conversion
    - Implemented rename_volume method for volume renaming
    - Added find_free_diskname helper for disk allocation
    - Uses __pve_base__ snapshot as template marker
  * Fixed: "storage definition has no path" error on template creation
    - Plugin now handles block storage template creation natively
    - No longer falls back to file-based create_base implementation
  * Fixed: list_images now correctly identifies template volumes
    - Template volumes return base-XXX-disk-X instead of vm-XXX-disk-X
    - Detection based on presence of __pve_base__ snapshot
  * Fixed: path() now handles missing LUNs gracefully
    - Returns synthetic path when LUN doesn't exist (orphaned volume)
    - Allows deletion of orphaned volumes via PVE UI
  * Added API.pm volume_rename method for ONTAP volume renaming

