jt-pve-storage-netapp (0.1.3-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * FlexClone Support Release
  * New Feature: Linked Clone via NetApp FlexClone
    - Template and linked clone now supported
    - Instant clone creation (no data copy needed)
    - Space-efficient: clones share unchanged blocks with parent
    - Automatic LUN identity for cloned volumes
    - FlexClone license check with helpful error message
  * Safety Improvements:
    - Prevent deletion of templates with clone children
    - Clear error message listing dependent clones
  * Bug Fixes:
    - Fixed path() method causing system hangs when device not accessible
    - path() now returns synthetic path when device not found locally
    - Allows deletion of VMs whose devices were never activated
    - Prevents kernel hung tasks caused by faulty multipath devices
  * Package Installation Improvements:
    - Fixed prerm script hanging during upgrade (added 5s timeout for pvesm)
    - Fixed postinst script potential hang (added timeout for systemctl calls)
    - All deb maintainer scripts now have proper timeout protection
  * Volume Sizing:
    - Enabled volume autogrow (expands automatically when needed)
    - Reduced initial overhead to 64MB
    - Volume max size set to 2x LUN size

